      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just feel like 5mg is a lot for someone as active as me now. i've been reading some stuff online about how if your lifestyle is really stable and you aren't eating lots of greens, you might not even need that much to keep things balanced. wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg over time actually be safer so i'm not way too thin on the blood? i just want to be more cautious with how much i'm taking.",
